WEBVTT

00:01.388 --> 00:03.028
Okay, you know what we're not
going to do?

00:03.053 --> 00:05.486
We're not going to shoot one of those
videos where we watch people die.

00:05.540 --> 00:10.943
Your father, how he loved to
see me get out of his car.

00:11.320 --> 00:13.855
Thank you for staying.

00:13.889 --> 00:14.989
Expecting somebody?

00:15.016 --> 00:16.383
Uh, no.

00:16.417 --> 00:18.318
Wrong address.

00:19.320 --> 00:21.287
And I know you are not
selling drugs

00:21.322 --> 00:22.355
out of this house.

00:22.390 --> 00:24.024
You know I'd never
do anything like that.

00:24.058 --> 00:26.926
I can meet you somewhere for a drink
unless you're meeting someone.

00:26.961 --> 00:28.028
Yeah, yeah, I am.

00:28.963 --> 00:31.131
- I'm sorry for hurting you.
- You said that.

00:31.165 --> 00:34.134
But I've never said
I'm filing for divorce.

00:34.168 --> 00:35.602
I told Avery today.

00:40.541 --> 00:42.409
That's not how it happened.

00:42.443 --> 00:43.777
You totally pursued me.

00:43.811 --> 00:45.278
You obviously knew who I was.

00:45.312 --> 00:46.780
Well, I watch CNN.

00:46.814 --> 00:48.481
Whatever.

00:48.516 --> 00:50.183
You really feeling
yourself, huh?

00:50.217 --> 00:52.952
I am on practically every
billboard around town.

00:52.987 --> 00:54.587
Come on now, let's be real.

00:54.622 --> 00:56.089
You would be at the gym,

00:56.123 --> 00:59.592
exercising and arching
your back just so

00:59.627 --> 01:01.127
you could
throw it all in my face.

01:01.162 --> 01:02.362
You know you were
feeling me first.

01:02.396 --> 01:05.131
I was not arching
my back in the gym.

01:05.166 --> 01:06.366
Who does that?

01:07.702 --> 01:09.803
Okay, maybe I did a little bit.
Yeah, exactly.

01:09.837 --> 01:11.738
It worked.

01:11.772 --> 01:14.107
You didn't tell me you were
married, though.

01:14.141 --> 01:15.408
Yeah, about that.

01:15.443 --> 01:18.011
I was too busy
watching your arch.

01:18.045 --> 01:20.013
Mm-hmm.
Mm-hmm.

01:20.047 --> 01:22.282
So you like the place?

01:22.316 --> 01:25.418
I mean, it's not done.
It will be done.

01:26.987 --> 01:28.822
Isn't that cool?

01:31.826 --> 01:33.460
That's what I wake up
to every morning.

01:33.494 --> 01:35.595
I always wanted a loft.

01:35.629 --> 01:39.032
And now you can stay over
at my place for a change.

01:40.267 --> 01:41.468
That'll be nice.

01:41.502 --> 01:43.002
I'd like that.

01:43.037 --> 01:44.637
How much you like it?

01:47.174 --> 01:48.942
How much?
Show me how much.

01:50.745 --> 01:52.145
Oh, that much?

01:52.179 --> 01:54.280
Kind of like this.
Kind of like that?

01:55.416 --> 01:56.483
Come back.

01:57.718 --> 01:58.952
Knock, knock!

01:58.986 --> 02:01.588
Hey, up here, up here.
We're all here?

02:01.622 --> 02:03.890
Mr. Daniels,
nice to see you.

02:03.924 --> 02:06.192
Good to see you too, Leanne.

02:06.227 --> 02:07.494
Watch your step.

02:07.528 --> 02:08.595
Thank you.

02:09.964 --> 02:11.631
Somebody I want you to meet.

02:11.665 --> 02:13.733
Uh, this is my lovely lady.

02:13.768 --> 02:15.568
Mary Jane, this is Leanne.

02:15.603 --> 02:16.903
Hi, a pleasure to meet you.

02:16.937 --> 02:18.037
I love your show.

02:18.072 --> 02:19.506
Oh, thank you.

02:19.540 --> 02:21.741
So the place is ready, right?

02:21.776 --> 02:23.510
I'm itching to move in.

02:23.544 --> 02:26.613
Unfortunately, it's not going
to be ready for another month.

02:26.647 --> 02:29.983
What happened to
around-the-clock?

02:30.017 --> 02:31.618
We were good in a week.

02:31.652 --> 02:33.386
Well, I do have a couple of
other vacancies

02:33.420 --> 02:35.121
coming up next month
that fit your specs.

02:35.156 --> 02:36.856
Oh, next month is no good.

02:36.891 --> 02:38.458
You're killing me, Leanne.

02:38.492 --> 02:40.293
Don't worry, Dre,
you'll find something.

02:42.263 --> 02:45.064
Can we, uh, have a moment?

02:45.099 --> 02:46.266
Oh, sure.

02:46.300 --> 02:48.134
Okay, appreciate it.

02:53.941 --> 02:55.842
It doesn't work, babe.

02:55.876 --> 02:57.443
I told her I need to
move out now.

02:59.180 --> 03:03.082
It means I'd have to stay in a
hotel, which I guess I could do.

03:04.428 --> 03:05.828
You're not going to
stay at a hotel.

03:05.853 --> 03:08.354
You'll stay with me
until this place is finished.

03:10.558 --> 03:11.891
She said a month.

03:11.926 --> 03:14.561
You sure?
I'm sure.

03:14.595 --> 03:16.529
This is what you want.

03:18.666 --> 03:20.600
Maybe I did
flirt with you first.

03:22.036 --> 03:23.436
You're too good for me.

